T* (<p>Audit report printed by Pankaj Khare on February 23rd 2024, 10:14:08 pm</p>) Tj
T* (<h2>Help with prison visits</h2>) Tj
T* (<p>This report covers the period 02 January 2001 to 02 January 2019.</p>) Tj
T* (<p>A total of 2 manually approved claims were checked, with 2 of these verified.</p>) Tj
T* (<p>The total amount checked was Ł105</p>) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (<h2>Claim checks</h2>) Tj
T* (<p>Of the 2 claims checked:</p>) Tj
T* (<ul>) Tj
T* (    <li>1 were found to be valid claims</li>) Tj
T* (    <li>1 were found to be invalid claims</li>) Tj
T* (</ul>) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (<h2>Claim verification</h2>) Tj
T* (<p>Of the 2 claims, 2 were randomly chosen for verification:</p>) Tj
T* (<ul>) Tj
T* (    <li>1 were confirmed to be valid claims</li>) Tj
T* (    <li>1 were found to be invalid claims</li>) Tj
T* (</ul>) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (<p>Of the 1 invalid claims all were sent for verification:</p>) Tj
T* (<ul>) Tj
T* (    <li>1 were confirmed to be invalid claims</li>) Tj
T* (    <li>0 were found to be valid claims</li>) Tj
T* (</ul>) Tj
